metadata.name: Violet13 #2
metadata.description: The first image of Violet originated from the darkest depths of a text-to-image algorithm. It spawned variants to arrive at a total of 13 initial images. The Violet13 were then dissected to into rarity traits. 1313 unique visions have been generated. This NFT collection lives forever more on the Ethereum blockchain.
